{"tid":2449582,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"sorry 好長氣 但真心想問下大家","createTime":"2021-03-16T20:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T16:48:48.000Z","uid":337484,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e353d50c1238592117d00ba195765fe857c5de16","tid":2449582,"uid":337484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T20:15:06.000Z","msg":"求求高人 指點迷津<br />\n<br />\n如果A同完B嗌交<br />\n而A應該就唔會再見到B<br />\n而B有時仲會wts A又或者callA 話想箍煲 想搞反好個關係 唔頻密嘅<br />\n（但有時 佢發起癲黎仲會無拉拉call A成廿次，但A都唔會接電話）<br />\nA會已讀不回B 就算B見到A藍tick佢  B wts都仲keep住sd msg俾A<br />\n好撚厚面皮<br />\n<br />\n睇到依度既各位高人，如果你係A，你會唔會block咗佢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> block 9 佢啦屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放佢係度唔理 覺得佢有一日會死心<br />\n<br />\n故事黎到今日為止<br />\nA係冇block到B ，而A keep住已讀不回<br />\n對於A個處理手法，你哋覺得係點解呢？<br />\n如果係你，你哋會點做？<br />\n因為我真係睇唔明<br />\n<br />\nA會唔會係因為仲care個B，而唔block佢？<br />\nB有冇機會再追反個A？<br />\nB應唔應該再搵A，定係要收皮，放過人哋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說<br />\n我就係B， <br />\n如果要屌我 細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌醒我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be7a9d52ed2065eb4a75fa8ae8c5cb171657b79","tid":2449582,"uid":89905,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T20:25:52.000Z","msg":"唔會，係鍾意你嘅一早復合咗。<br />\n佢只係鍾意有人鍾意佢/追佢嘅感覺。"},{"pid":"61201531b8939a852c6ec79869396bb110ce303b","tid":2449582,"uid":205566,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T20:29:35.000Z","msg":"唔blk你係因為當你笑話，cap 你講d嘢share比d fd一齊笑吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7eddfc97a5c3992fdd57f70f0db8aca01e1607","tid":2449582,"uid":307877,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T20:30:43.000Z","msg":"收手啦傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf75a463dea75fee9934cece23ae5200abafbf6f","tid":2449582,"uid":337484,"li